metadata.name: DefiMap: Pioneer Member Pass
metadata.description:
All aboard explorers,
DefiMap is your ultimate DeFi strategies database, providing you with accurate analysis, real yields, and easy-to-understand visualizations. With DefiMap, you can explore a range of investment strategies, benchmark them against others, and manage risks like a pro with traditional risk insights.

Start Here: https://defimap.app/


DefiMap: Pioneer Pass is DefiMap's first NFT to commemorate its first beta launch. Holders of Pioneer Pass will be considered on the waitlist to get priority access to the upcoming features from DefiMap.

As a thank you for our early users who are waitlisted, holders will be able to claim Gold Pioneer Member pass in the future.

Gold Pioneer Member Pass benefits are:
Early access to all new DefiMap features
3 Months free for all paid features
Gold Pioneer member pass NFT
50% off for 12 months on all paid features
Priority support channel
+ Much more benefits in the future!

To claim Gold Pioneer Member Pass please keep an eye on our twitter or email.
At DefiMap we aim to help users find the best strategies for their portfolio. Follow our product updates, news or give us suggestions via the channel listed below.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/DeFi_Map
Telegram: http://t.me/defimap

Godspeed explorers,
Defimap Team
